<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>ComplianceOS India Demo</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: #0b0d0f;
      color: #f7f6f4;
    }
    header {
      background: #111316;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }
    header h1 {
      font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin: 0;
      color: #bfa36a;
    }
    header p {
      color: #cfd3d6;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }
    .hero {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 3rem auto;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .cta {
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .cta a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .cta .primary {
      background: #bfa36a;
      color: #0b0d0f;
    }
    .cta .secondary {
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      color: #cfd3d6;
    }
    .dashboard {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 3rem auto;
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }
    .card {
      background: #0f1316;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(2,6,23,0.65);
    }
    .card h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #bfa36a;
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      color: #cfd3d6;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>ComplianceOS India</h1>
    <p>Regulatory clarity for Indian business</p>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <h2>Know what applies. Act before it hurts.</h2>
    <p>Citation‑backed compliance intelligence for founders, advisors, and enterprise teams.</p>
    <div class="cta">
      <a href="#" class="primary">Start Assessment</a>
      <a href="#" class="secondary">Request Demo</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="dashboard">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Compliance Posture Score</h3>
      <p><strong>72%</strong> — Moderate risk exposure</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Mandatory Now</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>GST Registration</li>
        <li>ESI Registration</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Approaching Deadlines</h3>
      <p>Annual Return — due in 14 days</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Threshold Watchlist</h3>
      <p>Employee count nearing 10 — ESI trigger</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Recent Updates</h3>
      <p>New GST notification published March 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    © 2026 ComplianceOS India — AI‑powered compliance applicability and workflow platform
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
